(29, '', 'پراگراف سن کر سوالات کے جوابات دیں۔', '', 'حضرت عمر فاروق رضی اللہ تعالیٰ عنہ مسلمانوں کے دوسرے خلیفہ تھے۔ آپ کا تعلق قریش کے معزز قبیلے بنو عدی سے تھا۔آپؐ کی دعا کے بل بوتے حضرت عمر رضی اللہ تعالیٰ عنہ نے اسلام قبول کیا۔ ان کی اسلام میں آمد کے بعد پہلی بار مسلمانوں نے خانہ کعبہ میں نماز ادا کی۔اس پر نبی پاکؐ نے انہیں فاروق کا لقب دیا۔حضرت ابوبکر رضی اللہ تعالیٰ عنہ کے بعد انہیں خلیفہ چن لیا گیا۔ آپ رات کے وقت گلیوں میں گشت کرتے۔حضرت عمر رضی اللہ تعالیٰ عنہ نے انصاف، ایثار اور فلاح وبہبود کے کاموں کی وجہ سے بہترین حکمران کا درجہ پایا۔آپ کا دور اسلامی تاریخ کا سنہری دور ہے۔ آپؐ نے فرمایا: قوم کا سردار قوم کا خادم ہوتا ہے۔حضرت عمر رضی اللہ تعالیٰ اس کی قوم کی عملی تصویر تھے۔', 'Top', NULL, 16, 7, 26, 605, 608, 612, 613, 619, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 4, 26, '2021-10-15 09:46:01', 3, 'ok', 0, '', 0, '', '2021-10-21 12:21:00', 6, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 0),
(30, 'Tick the correct word, phrase or sentence to answer the questions.   ', '', 'Life in the Desert<br />\r\nThere are different kinds of deserts. There are hot deserts and there are cold deserts. The Sahara Desert is the largest hot desert in the world. The Gobi Desert is always very cold. Some deserts are sandy. Some deserts are rocky. Other deserts have mountains. A desert is a very dry place. It has very little rain. There can be sandstorms or snowstorms. In sandy deserts, the wind blows the sand and forms sand dunes. A sand dune is a mountain of sand. Plants and animals need water to survive in hot deserts. Although these deserts are very dry, it is amazing how many plants live there. People often travel to the desert on camels. Camels have humps on their backs in which they carry food. They can drink a lot of water at once and then, they do not need to drink for a very long time. They have thick fur to keep them warm at night when it is cold. They are perfect for desert life.<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '', 'Top', NULL, 16, 7, 25, 1082, 1085, 1087, 1091, 1148, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<strong>Directions</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Explain that, Information about deserts will be read out. Students should listen carefully as they will be asked to complete activities after they are listening to it.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;After listening students will look at the worksheet given by the teacher to skim and scan. Read the instructions after the first reading and follow this with the second reading. Allow time for the students to complete task.</li>\r\n	<li>Do not answer students questions or clarify anything, simply repeat each instruction. Do not repeat the instructions in the middle of the task.</li>\r\n	<li>Worksheet will be given before listening will be started.</li>\r\n	<li>Each correct answer will be awarded 2 marks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, 1, 14, '2021-10-17 16:26:06', 0, '', 0, '', 0, '', NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 0);
